OL,3,CPolice hunt wanted fraudster after
OL,4,Cheritage railway scammed out of
OL,5,Cthousands
OL,7,FA heritage railway between Bristol and
OL,8,FBath says it's been scammed out of
OL,9,F#50,000 pounds by a wanted fraudster
OL,10,Fwho posed as an employee.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Avon Valley Railway
OL,13,Fsaid it began to notice several
OL,14,Ffinancial irregularities after the
OL,15,Fresignation of employee Matthew Smith.
OL,17,FAfter investigating further, it found
OL,18,Fbigger problems which it believed to
OL,19,Fbe deliberate acts of fraud.
