OL,3,CPolice hunt wanted fraudster after
OL,4,Cheritage railway scammed out of
OL,5,Cthousands
OL,7,FThe Avon Valley Railway Heritage
OL,8,FTrust, a volunteer-led charity which
OL,9,Fruns the Avon Valley Railway reported
OL,10,Fits findings to the police.
OL,12,FFollowing investigation, it was
OL,13,Fdiscovered that Matthew Smith's true
OL,14,Fidentity was Nathan Hudson - a wanted
OL,15,Fcareer criminal with a long history of
OL,16,Fscamming operations in Humberside and
OL,17,FEdinburgh, among other locations since
OL,18,F2003.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
