OL,3,CPolice hunt wanted fraudster after
OL,4,Cheritage railway scammed out of
OL,5,Cthousands
OL,7,FAvon Valley Railway has now launched a
OL,8,Ffundraiser to help rebuild its
OL,9,Ffinances. It says colleagues have been
OL,10,Femotionally and financially impacted
OL,11,Fby Hudson's alleged actions.
OL,13,FIn a statement, it said: "Every penny
OL,14,Fdonated is massively appreciated at
OL,15,Fthis time. After the resignation of
OL,16,FMatthew Smith, a previously well-
OL,17,Fpresented and respected employee of
OL,18,FAvon Valley Railway Company Ltd, the
OL,19,Frailway has been horrified to find
OL,20,Fwhat initially appeared to be a few
OL,21,Ffinancial irregularities.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
