OL,3,CPolice hunt wanted fraudster after
OL,4,Cheritage railway scammed out of
OL,5,Cthousands
OL,7,F"Hudson created fake profiles and
OL,8,Fappears to have fabricated supporting
OL,9,Fdocumentation to maintain the illusion
OL,10,Fof his false identity. He used his
OL,11,Fwell-liked character to gain trust and
OL,12,Fbuild 'friendships' with staff and
OL,13,Fvolunteers across the organisation.
OL,15,F"Some staff and volunteers have also
OL,16,Fbeen financially impacted. This is
OL,17,Flikely a strategy he had successfully
OL,18,Femployed in his numerous previous
OL,19,Fscams.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
