OL,3,CPolice hunt wanted fraudster after
OL,4,Cheritage railway scammed out of
OL,5,Cthousands
OL,7,F"After an in-depth investigation it is
OL,8,Fnow apparent that the Railway has been
OL,9,Fimpacted by approximately #50,000, as
OL,10,Fa consequence of the activities of
OL,11,Fthis person.
OL,13,F"This has affected its ability to
OL,14,Fundertake much of its planned
OL,15,Frestoration and maintenance work over
OL,16,Fthe winter. The railway can not be
OL,17,Fcertain that during the time of his
OL,18,Femployment he did not have external
OL,19,Fassistance for his fraudulent
OL,20,Factivities."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
