OL,7,FThe railway's Chairman Roger Eynon
OL,8,Fadded: "It's been a difficult few
OL,9,Fmonths for all of us and we're working
OL,10,Fhard to recover from Matthew Smith/
OL,11,FNathan Hudson's actions.
OL,13,F"We're launching our Bounce Back
OL,14,Fappeal to enable us to continue our
OL,15,Fvital restoration work this year and
OL,16,Fbeyond so any money we receive is so
OL,17,Fmassively appreciated at this time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
