OL,3,CPolice hunt wanted fraudster after
OL,4,Cheritage railway scammed out of
OL,5,Cthousands
OL,7,F"The actions of this person have had a
OL,8,Fsevere personal impact on the
OL,9,Fvolunteers, staff and management of
OL,10,Fthe railway, who trusted him and
OL,11,Fthought of him as a friend and valued
OL,12,Fcolleague, making it a difficult and
OL,13,Fstressful time for all of us.
OL,15,F"We are working hard to recover from
OL,16,Fthe situation and look forward to a
OL,17,Fmore positive 2025 - but we need your
OL,18,Fhelp."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
